  "title": "Food Production Packer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Highlights</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Staff lunch provided</li>\n  <li>In-house gym</li>\n  <li>Short walking distance from Tuas Link MRT</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p>We are looking for reliable and detail-oriented Food Production Packers to join our team. You will be responsible for packing food products safely and efficiently, ensuring they meet our quality and food safety standards.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Duties &amp; Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Pack and label food products according to company specifications and orders</li>\n  <li>Perform visual quality checks on products before packing</li>\n  <li>Assemble and prepare packaging materials as needed</li>\n  <li>Assist in loading and stacking finished goods on pallets or storage areas</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of the packing area and equipment</li>\n  <li>Follow food safety, hygiene, and workplace safety guidelines at all times</li>\n  <li>Support other production-related duties assigned by supervisors</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>No prior experience required – training provided</li>\n  <li>Preferably some experience in food production, packing, or warehouse environment</li>\n  <li>Physically fit and able to work standing for extended periods</li>\n  <li>Able to handle repetitive tasks with attention to detail</li>\n  <li>Responsible, punctual, and able to work well in a team</li>\n</ul>",
